text: Ieva Krasnova (born 7 May 2001) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a forward for Sieviešu Futbola Līga club FK Dinamo Rīga and the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers
